text.section:
On or before the date that an applicant submits a corrective action plan to the cabinet, the applicant shall:
Notify local government units affected by the remediation of the provisions of the corrective action plan;
Provide a copy of the corrective action plan to at least one (1) public library in any county affected by the remediation;
Submit for publication in a newspaper of general circulation in the county or counties where the property is located, a notice requesting public comment on the corrective action plan, and submit to the cabinet a copy of the notice as published, within ten (10) days of its publication; and
Post a sign on the property stating that the site is undergoing remediation and providing information on where and when the corrective action plan is available for public review and comment.
